 now easier than ever. With Typography Styles, you can add detailed code blocks to explain your customizations effectively. You can make your code blocks as long as necessary.`<\/span>);\n}<\/code><\/span><small class=\"shcb-language\" id=\"shcb-language-2\"><span class=\"shcb-language__label\">Code language:<\/span> <span class=\"shcb-language__name\">JavaScript<\/span> <span class=\"shcb-language__paren\">(<\/span><span class=\"shcb-language__slug\">javascript<\/span><span class=\"shcb-language__paren\">)<\/span><\/small><\/pre>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"lists\">Lists<\/h3>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph \" style=\"\">Typography Styles ensures that ordered and unordered lists look good by default, allowing you to create organized and appealing lists:<\/p>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Lists are easy to read.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lists maintain visual appeal.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Your WordPress content stays well-organized.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Ordered lists are clear and concise.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Each item is numbered for clarity.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can have as many list items as needed.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>More items make your content informative.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>This is item number five.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Continue adding more items.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Seven is a lucky number.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add more to enrich your content.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The ninth item provides additional detail.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"nested-lists\">Nested Lists<\/h3>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph \" style=\"\">Nested lists are also styled for readability and aesthetics. Here&#8217;s a more extensive example:<\/p>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Nested lists should be used thoughtfully.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They can create complex shapes on the screen.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keeping your content flat is often best.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoid nesting lists too deeply.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>More items to ensure realistic styling.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Two levels of nesting are usually sufficient.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Three levels can be too complex.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoid four levels for better readability.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>A second item to maintain interest.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Let&#8217;s keep the list growing.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can have many levels of nesting.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Each level adds depth to your content.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>This is the third item in the list.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list \">\n<li>Consistency is important.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nested lists are for specific scenarios.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use them wisely.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"tables\">Tables<\/h3>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph \" style=\"\">Typography Styles ensures your tables are visually appealing and easy to read:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th>Plugin Name<\/th><th>Description<\/th><th>Rating<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Akismet<\/td><td>Spam protection for your site<\/td><td>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Yoast SEO<\/td><td>Improve your WordPress SEO<\/td><td>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>WooCommerce<\/td><td>E-commerce solution for WordPress<\/td><td>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Elementor<\/td><td>Drag-and-drop page builder for WordPress<\/td><td>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>W3 Total Cache<\/td><td>Speed up your site with caching<\/td><td>\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"links\">Links<\/h2>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph \" style=\"\">Typography Styles offers a modern look for links, making them visually appealing. For example, <a href=\"https:\/\/typographystyles.com\">this link to Typography Styles<\/a> is styled to perfection, with a dark gray color that adds a touch of elegance.<\/p>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"conclusion\">Conclusion<\/h2>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph \" style=\"\">Typography Styles simplifies WordPress typography, making it easy to style your content without the need for complex CSS. With Typography Styles, your WordPress content will look beautiful, readable, and well-organized. Use it to create stunning WordPress content with ease.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This post is an introduction on how to create and style content in the WordPress editor.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":14995,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14762"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14762"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14762\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14995"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14762"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14762"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.blockifywp.com\/codeify\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14762"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org